OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,FSouthampton striker Ross Stewart says
OL,7,Fthe club are ready for what boss Tonda
OL,8,FEckert calls "prime time" as the
OL,9,Fpromotion hopefuls look for some FA
OL,10,FCup magic against Manchester City,
OL,11,Fhalf a century on from lifting the
OL,12,Ftrophy.
OL,14,FSaints are parking their Championship
OL,15,Fcharge on Saturday and heading to
OL,16,FWembley for a mouth-watering semi-
OL,17,Ffinal as they seek to shock Pep
OL,18,FGuardiola's side in the same way they
OL,19,Fstunned Arsenal in the previous round.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
