OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,FThat quarter-final shock came during a
OL,7,Frun of eight-straight wins in all
OL,8,Fcompetitions and forms part of an
OL,9,Fongoing unbeaten run that reached a
OL,10,F20th match with Tuesday's frustrating
OL,11,F2-2 draw with Bristol City.
OL,13,FSouthampton's automatic promotion
OL,14,Fhopes appear to be over after that
OL,15,Fresult, but Stewart is keeping things
OL,16,Fin perspective as they take on City in
OL,17,Fwhat could be the first of three trips
OL,18,Fto Wembley over the next month, with
OL,19,Fthe FA Cup and play-offs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,F"We're in a really good place right
OL,7,Fnow going into what the manager says
OL,8,Fis prime time, which is the really
OL,9,Fimportant part of the season," the
OL,10,FSaints striker said.
OL,12,F"It's when you can obviously make or
OL,13,Fbreak your season and we want to go
OL,14,Fand get promoted so it's a really
OL,15,Fimportant stage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,F"I watched City at the weekend against
OL,7,FArsenal. They were incredible in that
OL,8,Fgame and they're obviously probably
OL,9,Fthe form team in the country at the
OL,10,Fminute (which) just adds the
OL,11,Fdifficulty of the task.
OL,13,F"But we're a really tough team to beat
OL,14,Fas well, so hopefully it sets up for a
OL,15,Freally good semi-final."
OL,17,F"We've had a really good cup run so
OL,18,Ffar and we don't want it to stop,"
OL,19,FStewart added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@XO]yD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
