OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,F"I hope a bit of that 50-year-old
OL,7,Fmagic is with us and we can go and
OL,8,Fkind of replicate it.
OL,10,F"It's going to be a tough ask but
OL,11,Fwe're in there. If we do a lot of
OL,12,Fthings that we've done against
OL,13,FArsenal, we can hopefully come out on
OL,14,Fthe right side."
OL,16,FStewart scored Southampton's opener in
OL,17,Fthe 2-1 quarter-final win against
OL,18,FPremier League title hopefuls Arsenal,
OL,19,Fhaving struck the late penalty that
OL,20,Fsecured a 1-0 victory at Fulham in the
OL,21,Fprevious round.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
