FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old also has fond memories
OL,7,Fof Wembley, where he scored in
OL,8,FSunderland's 2022 League One play-off
OL,9,Fwin before being part of the Saints
OL,10,Fteam promoted there from the
OL,11,FChampionship, two years on.
OL,13,F"Luckily, I've had fond memories of
OL,14,FWembley.
OL,16,F"Both play-off finals that I've played
OL,17,Fin and, yeah, it'll be good to go
OL,18,Fback," Stewart said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777136757
OL,3,CSaints striker Ross Stewart: 'I hope a
OL,4,Cbit of 50-year magic is with us'
OL,6,F"It's obviously slightly different
OL,7,Fthis time and you're playing probably
OL,8,Fthe best team in the country, but
OL,9,Fhopefully I can use a bit of that
OL,10,Fexperience to manage myself and put in
OL,11,Fa good performance, if and when I'm
OL,12,Fcalled upon.
OL,14,F"Hopefully as a team, we can go there
OL,15,Fand do ourselves justice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@ZO]
